Sappi to Sell $680 Million of Bonds to Repay Existing Debt

-- B y   A n t o n y   S g u a z z i n
-- 
2011-04-04T06:34:10Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-04/sappi-to-sell-680-million-of-bonds-to-repay-existing-debt.html
Sappi Ltd. (SAP)  said it will sell $680
million worth of bonds to repay existing debt.  The new bonds will be sold in two tranches maturing in 2018
and 2021.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Antony Sguazzin at 
 asguazzin@bloomberg.net  